Finally, let me note, the work

174
00:07:52.545 --> 00:07:54.305
of the Infrastructure practitioners group,

175
00:07:55.165 --> 00:07:58.185
its submission brings together cross sector technical input

176
00:07:58.445 --> 00:08:01.905
across telecommunications, energy, transport, health

177
00:08:01.965 --> 00:08:04.025
and education infrastructure providers

178
00:08:04.025 --> 00:08:07.145
that really have had the opportunity to, uh, come together.

179
00:08:07.365 --> 00:08:11.065
And what struck me was the alignment of feedback across

180
00:08:11.065 --> 00:08:12.105
